{"tid":1645460,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"15 year-old protestor found dead at Yau Tong","createTime":"2019-10-11T01:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T11:13:31.000Z","uid":222614,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a7a48a29ee252deda310018abda1d52552a00831","tid":1645460,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:44:21.000Z","msg":"A 15 year-old girl has gone missing since 19 September. The police confirmed that the body found at Yau Tong is believed to be a 15 year-old girl who was earlier reported missing. However, the police did not further confirm her full name.<br />\n<br />\nAccording to several persons closed to the teenage girl, the body found is the missing girl called Chan Yin Lam. They also revealed that Chan was a swimmer and she has participated in many protests related to anti ELAB.<br />\n<br />\nVTC also confirmed that Chan was one of their students and that she has passed away.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/06zVukv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06zVukv.jpg&h=a3eb75de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOriginal news:<br />\n網上流傳一則15歲失蹤少女陳彥霖的尋人啟事，她自9月19日失蹤多天仍未尋回，網民紛表憂心，近日網上有留言指她「已經死咗，變咗浮屍」。警方接受《蘋果》查詢時證實，9月22日在油塘魔鬼山一帶海面發現一具全裸女浮屍，調查後相信為15歲陳姓失蹤女童，但未有進一步確認浮屍是否陳彥霖。彥霖多個身邊人向《蘋果》確認，警方發現的浮屍就是彥霖，不過她本身是游泳健將，生前又經常「發夢」，多次參與反修例示威，憂慮死因有可疑。職訓局（VTC）確認陳彥霖是該校學生，並證實其死訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191011/60139820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191011%2F60139820&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=5615da9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191011%2F60139820&h=aabbc9d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191011/60139820</a>"},{"pid":"574eb46652211c44d4d65809ed1826db083a93de","tid":1645460,"uid":332832,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:03:37.000Z","msg":"This story broke my heart and brought tears to my eyes. <br />\n<br />\nMay she Rest In Peace."},{"pid":"3a3732b5bba632be574094c314cb4180543e7197","tid":1645460,"uid":241567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T03:01:52.000Z","msg":"we need the truth. why she died."},{"pid":"64214e8fee5e083251dc6675ccdb76b0169e1b48","tid":1645460,"uid":231090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:10:13.000Z","msg":"Sad to hear this news in the morning.<br />\nAt least,we could know one of floated dead bodies is our friend.<br />\nIt is too suspicious,especially she excels in swimming but you told me she was dead because of drowning.<br />\nHope we could reveal for her and the other victims someday.<br />\nRIP"},{"pid":"0593afb624149d8abfa158723191a8560eaa7340","tid":1645460,"uid":61101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:12:26.000Z","msg":"murdered by popo <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33cfa2cdca8a17a15476e93562ba47eda94b1621","tid":1645460,"uid":308226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"If this poor girl really took suicide, then how do you explain she was being naked<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> The truth is quite obvious guys<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8187db2d69681c3609f62774385fe4e29622aa72","tid":1645460,"uid":308226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64214e8fee5e083251dc6675ccdb76b0169e1b48","tid":1645460,"uid":231090,"like":0,"dis